40|$|Kayleigh GarthwaiteStigmatising and dehumanising {{language}} {{directed at}} people receiving benefits {{might be good}} politics but it is bad policy, writes Kayleigh Garthwaite. Her {{research has focused on}} the narratives of 25 <b>sick</b> <b>and</b> disabled <b>benefits</b> recipients, and she finds that their circumstances are far different than what government rhetoric and mass media portrayals suggest...|$|R
